---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-gradient relative py-28 md:py-36 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Decorative background elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 -left-32 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-primary/10 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 -right-32 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-primary-light/10 blur-3xl"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">
        Consulting and Advisory Services
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-white/90">
        Expertise and Solutions for Your Every Need
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-mesh">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
        <p>
          X4O (Pty) Limited provides a variety of innovative and comprehensive solutions by tapping into the domain knowledge of a number of industry experts. We deliver quality services in the most efficient way, and our experts will work collaboratively with you to customize our offerings to support you to define and achieve your ideal future state.
        </p>
        <p class="font-semibold" style="color: #174069;">
          Contact us to find out how we can assist you to achieve your strategic goals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Sections -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-mesh">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-16">

      <!-- 1. Project and Programme Management -->
      <div id="project-management" class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 scroll-mt-24">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #174069;">
            Project and Programme Management
          </h2>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #174069;">What You Need</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Our Programme and Project management track record is the basis of our confidence that we can assist you with implementing a Delivery Framework, skilling up your employees with real-world experience or delivering your strategic projects using tools that enables efficiency and value creation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Advisory -->
      <div id="advisory" class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 scroll-mt-24">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #174069;">
            Advisory
          </h2>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #174069;">How We Help</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8">
          In today's hyper-connected world, organizations are challenged in more ways than ever to stay ahead of the curve. Finding the right partners to deliver effectively is increasing in complexity as the economic and technology landscape expands and the competencies evolve. We use our combined experience working at a global level within the Public and Private sector industries to assist you to achieve your business needs without disrupting productivity or workflow. X4O (Pty) Limited is sure to help your organization succeed.
        </p>

        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #174069;">Areas of Expertise</h4>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Infrastructure</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Municipal Infrastructure Development</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">General Manufacturing</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">New Emerging Industries</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Energy</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">The Digital Economy</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Digital Transformation</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Water and Sanitation</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Human Settlements</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Renewable Energy</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Natural Gas</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Green Hydrogen</span>
          <span class="glass rounded-lg px-4 py-2 text-sm text-center font-medium text-gray-700">Chemical Products</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Renewable Energy Advisory -->
      <div id="renewable-energy" class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 scroll-mt-24">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-primary-dark" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #174069;">
            Renewable Energy Advisory
          </h2>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #174069;">What We Can Do</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
          We have extensive experience as an advisor to the IDC and being a Transactional Advisor with experience focussing on:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 text-base">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Project development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Conceptual engineering design</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Financial modelling</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Lender engagement support</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>IPP proposal development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Municipal IPP Engagements</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>PPA advisory and contract negotiations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>EPC Contractor procurement strategy development</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Construction monitoring and project execution support</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Generator licensing and registration</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary shrink-0"></span>
            <span>Operations and Maintenance strategy development and support</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="hero-gradient py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Ready to discuss your project?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10">
        Let us help you achieve your strategic goals
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-lg">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
